    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278160/extras/d311996b0a677756dd4db0f6b2f1aa87.poster.avif?t=1730459701\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278160/extras/d311996b0a677756dd4db0f6b2f1aa87.webm?t=1730459701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278160/extras/d311996b0a677756dd4db0f6b2f1aa87.mp4?t=1730459701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fatal delivery is a short, first-person horror survival game. Play as a delivery driver in a semi-apocalyptic world who must take a strange package to a nearby city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monitor the health of your car and keep it in working condition as you navigate the highway at dusk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278160/extras/24d9b2a55210f8ca0fb505d2fbe9b88e.poster.avif?t=1730459701\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278160/extras/24d9b2a55210f8ca0fb505d2fbe9b88e.webm?t=1730459701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278160/extras/24d9b2a55210f8ca0fb505d2fbe9b88e.mp4?t=1730459701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features 10-15 minutes of gameplay with a total of 4 endings.</p>",
